data.description: This charming, move-in ready, story & a half, three bedroom home is centrally located in Effingham on a nearly quarter acre, oversized lot. You'll enter the home from a full width, covered brick porch, into the spacious living room with generous natural light. Notice the original hardwood millwork built-ins, including two window seats with enclosed storage, throughout the home. The refreshed eat-in kitchen offers great space for gatherings or entertainment, with tile floor, ample cabinet space, and all appliances remaining. The upstairs, oversized loft bedroom boasts amazing light, 2 walk-in closets, with a spaciousness only limited by your imagination. The partial basement includes mechanicals, laundry hook-ups, and plenty of built-in storage. The rear yard includes: a large attached back deck, garden shed, fire ring, extra parking, and space to roam. Come check out your dream home today!
